{"title":"[Swift]TextField 글자수 제한하기","date":"2020-05-21T15:33:59.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 21, 2020","L":"05/21/2020","MM-DD":"05-21"},"link":"2020/05/21/Swift-TextField-글자수-제한하기","tags":["TextField","TextFieldDelegate","로그인화면"],"categories":["ios"],"updated":"2020-08-20T01:08:23.380Z","content":"<p>TextFieldDelegate 사용시 텍스트필드에 글자수 제한두기</p>\n<p>아래의 코드만 붙여넣기하면 된다.</p>\n<p>🤷🏻‍♀️</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight swift\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//텍스트필드 글자수 제한</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">textField</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"number\">_</span> textField: UITextField, shouldChangeCharactersIn range: NSRange, replacementString string: String)</span></span> -&gt; <span class=\"type\">Bool</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">guard</span> <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> text = textField.text <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123; <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span> &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> newLength = text.<span class=\"built_in\">count</span> + string.<span class=\"built_in\">count</span> - range.length</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> newLength &lt;= <span class=\"number\">16</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>newLength &lt;= 16<br>\n의 16은 16자까지 제한 둔다는 뜻.</p>\n","prev":{"title":"[Swift]Fram과 AutoLayout을 이용한 다양한 방법들","link":"2020/05/21/Swift-Fram과-AutoLayout을-이용한-다양한-방법들"},"next":{"title":"[Swift]TextField에 밑줄 긋기","link":"2020/05/21/Swift-textField에-밑줄-긋기"